headline: Listen: Fauci Must’ve Had a Rough Nights Sleep…His Newest Move Today Suggests He’s Deeply Afraid of Midterms
author: Missy Crane
sentences:
MORE NEWS: Everyone Notices Something Very Strange About The Photo of Joe Biden in The Briefing Room Today
We did a piece last night that talked about how scared Fauci was sounding over the very real prospect that Republicans would be taking over Congress.

If anyone deserves to be PROBED with a 10-foot steel pole, it’s Fauci… and he also deserves to spend the rest of his miserable life behind bars for his “gain of function” research… we all know what he was doing, and we all know why, as well.

He’s convinced that he’ll be getting the “Benghazi treatment.”
Well, I guess he’s had a night to sleep on it, and now, he’s not just talking about Benghazi-style hearings… Now, he says retirement is on the table.

I have a feeling that the Democrat’s internal polling is so bad, that no matter what, they know they’re getting their clocks cleaned and they’ve sent out the warning signals to their most vulnerable crooks.
He can retire, and hope that things just “go away” and everyone forgets about him, but we will never forget, and I am pretty sure Jim Jordan and Rand Paul will never forget either.
Fauci is really nervous as we inch closer and closer to the midterms.

Fauci can run, but he can’t hide.
